---
import "../styles/global.css";
import Header from "../components/Header/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer/Footer.astro";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Monthly Event | Broken Duck Studio</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <Header />

    <main class="container" style="padding: 4rem 1.5rem; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <h1 style="font-size: 2.25rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Monthly YouTube Networking Event</h1>

      <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #ccc; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        On the last Sunday of every month, Broken Duck Studio opens its doors to the public for a free networking event focused on YouTube creators, production teams, editors, and anyone working in or around video content.
      </p>

      <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        Whether you're a full-time YouTuber, just getting started, or supporting creators behind the scenes, you're welcome here. The event is casual but focused — expect structured breakout introductions, gear talk, content planning chats, and plenty of chances to meet others working in the space.
      </p>

      <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        You don’t need to be a member to attend. Just show up, grab a drink, and introduce yourself. Bring a notebook, some questions, or a demo of what you’re working on.
      </p>

      <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 3rem;">Event Details</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left: 1.25rem; line-height: 1.8; margin-top: 1rem;">
        <li><strong>When:</strong> Last Sunday of each month</li>
        <li><strong>Time:</strong> 1:00pm – 4:00pm</li>
        <li><strong>Where:</strong> Broken Duck Studio, Pong Noi, Chiang Mai</li>
        <li><strong>Who Can Attend:</strong> Anyone interested in YouTube, video, or creative production</li>
        <li><strong>Cost:</strong> Free</li>
      </ul>

      <p style="margin-top: 2rem;">
        If you're a studio member, this is your chance to connect with potential collaborators. If you're not a member, it's a low-pressure way to meet the people behind the space and see what we're about.
      </p>
    </main>

    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
